WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.480
Did you know that many sleep problems start with an aging or unsupportive mattress?

00:04.480 --> 00:08.000
Our bodies change over the years, but our mattress usually doesn't.

00:08.000 --> 00:12.160
If it's been seven to ten years since you changed your mattress, maybe it's time to swap it out.

00:12.160 --> 00:15.680
I've found some mattress options that are perfect for you based on your responses.

